How do I update this listing?




                                             Legion Partners Asset Management is based out of Beverly Hills. Legion Partners Asset Management is a hedge fund  with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $168,300,000 (Form ADV from 2017-03-23).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $182,688,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 96.72%. Legion Partners Asset Management's largest holding is Banc of California with shares held of 2,812,579.   WhaleWisdom has at least 2 13Fs and  34 13D/G filings in our database for Legion Partners Asset Management. 
                                           














