H)Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC sold out the holdings in 1347 Property Insurance Holdings Inc. The sale prices were between $6.5 and $8.1, with an estimated average price of $7.18.Sold Out: Key Technology Inc (KTEC)Legion Partners Asset Management, LLC sold out the holdings in Key Technology Inc. The sale prices were between $11.71 and $13.85, with an estimated average price of $12.79.Warning! GuruFocus has detected 5 Warning Signs with BANC. Click here to check it out.BANC 15-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of BANCPeter Lynch Chart of BANCPremium MembersThis article first appeared on GuruFocus .



